# 🎨 Styling & UI Guidelines

## 🎯 Tailwind CSS Rules
- ✅ **Utility-first approach** - Use Tailwind classes
- ✅ **Mobile-first responsive design** - `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`, `2xl:`
- ✅ **CSS Variables** - Use design system colors (`text-primary`, `bg-background`)
- ✅ **Consistent spacing** - Use spacing scale (`space-y-4`, `p-6`, `gap-4`)
- ❌ **Avoid custom CSS** - Prefer Tailwind utilities

## 🎨 Design System Colors
```css
/* Primary Colors */
text-primary, bg-primary
text-secondary, bg-secondary
text-accent, bg-accent

/* Status Colors */
text-success, bg-success
text-warning, bg-warning
text-destructive, bg-destructive

/* Neutral Colors */
text-foreground, bg-background
text-muted-foreground, bg-muted
text-card-foreground, bg-card
```

## 📱 Responsive Design Patterns
```tsx
// Container with responsive padding
<div className="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-6xl">

// Responsive grid
<div className="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">

// Responsive text sizes
<h1 className="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">

// Responsive spacing
<div className="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">
```

## 🧩 Component Styling Patterns
```tsx
// Card component with hover effects
<Card className="p-6 space-y-4 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">

// Button with icon and responsive text
<Button size="sm" className="flex items-center space-x-1">
  <Icon className="h-4 w-4" />
  <span className="hidden sm:inline">Text</span>
</Button>

// Conditional styling
<div className={`p-4 rounded-lg ${
  isActive 
    ? "bg-primary text-primary-foreground" 
    : "bg-muted text-muted-foreground"
}`}>
```

## 🎭 Animation & Transitions
- **Hover Effects**: `hover:shadow-lg`, `hover:bg-muted/50`
- **Transitions**: `transition-all`, `transition-colors`
- **Loading States**: `animate-pulse`, `animate-spin`
- **Smooth Interactions**: `duration-200`, `ease-in-out`

## 📐 Layout Guidelines
- **Flexbox**: `flex items-center justify-between`
- **Grid**: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- **Spacing**: Consistent use of `space-y-*`, `gap-*`
- **Borders**: `border`, `border-border`, `rounded-lg`